{"tid":998114,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"渣打銀行其實好撚好用！","createTime":"2019-01-27T16:54:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T04:46:02.000Z","uid":232259,"like":17,"dislike":235,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"fced8cb4c7a5c6be5f8297d99974104b9d4e4533","tid":998114,"uid":232259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"上網見到啲人成日話渣打好垃圾 我自己手上有恆生卡 中銀卡 渣打卡 渣打卡係我心目中係無可替代！！我本身會上淘寶買野 但次次都要去7仔增值好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 渣打可以直接增值支付寶 等幾秒就有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 增幾多都得 我試過增10蚊都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外 因為我係用iphone 無nfc 所以冇得用電話增值八達通，但係渣打係可以增值八達通，都係等幾秒，我試過增十蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 7仔最小都50啦 有時仲要排隊 手上冇錢又要eps拎錢先增值到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我電話費 屋企上網都係用渣打交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n網上銀行轉帳去其他銀行好似係唔需要手續費 依個我就唔係好清楚<br />\n總之對我黎講真係好撚方便！"},{"pid":"4272193a097cfbe868e31d2734ef1d57902405d2","tid":998114,"uid":36136,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:55:49.000Z","msg":"有邊間做唔到你所講既野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f533bc796b7c8977abcee625305ba5da439e7895","tid":998114,"uid":78683,"like":78,"dislike":1,"score":77,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"懷疑樓主係渣打職員"},{"pid":"c7bb19882adfce7c125cbe42bbd025f600d45a97","tid":998114,"uid":115700,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T17:04:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾 ebanking"},{"pid":"1633dc869413c5e46630ba2d20b8de10c2a61503","tid":998114,"uid":232259,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"quote":{"pid":"4272193a097cfbe868e31d2734ef1d57902405d2","tid":998114,"uid":36136,"like":112,"dislike":2,"score":110,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T16:55:49.000Z